title: Steelers defensive end Cameron Heyward will discontinue tribute on eye back
text:
Published By: Pittsburgh Post: Steelers - Yesterday 
Steelers defensive end Cameron Heyward will no longer wear eye black honoring his late father after a hearing with the NFL today....
